{"tid":531782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"格魯吉亞核廢料事故","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T14:16:17.000Z","uid":73945,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5257fe270befd20a29f0d7d7a34bf539cb97727","tid":531782,"uid":73945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:44:20.000Z","msg":"熱電偶效應係指當兩種金屬接埋一齊，係接合位加熱就會產生電壓<br />\n可以用黎做温度計，亦都可以直接當電池<br />\n放射性同位素熱電機就係用一大舊放射性物質發熱黎做電池<br />\n好處係輸出大，可以去到幾百W，壽命可以有10－20年<br />\nNANA有D太空船，人造衞星就係用佢做電池<br />\n前蘇聯偏遠地方燈塔連電線都沒，太陽能又唔夠哥陣，都係用佢黎推着盞燈<br />\n<br />\n格魯吉亞係2001年有兩舊呢D野被不當棄置係野外<br />\n有3個村民發現有兩舊野識得發熱，於是當係暖包訓係隔離過夜<br />\n幾個鐘後又頭痛又嘔，返去睇醫生先揭發事件<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎<br />\n舊野放射性高達1Sv/h，當地政府究竟係點派人去回收件野<br />\n<br />\n下邊係一份IAEA report，講返成件事出黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www-pub.iaea.org/MTCD/Publications/PDF/Pub1660web-81061875.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww-pub.iaea.org%2FMTCD%2FPublications%2FPDF%2FPub1660web-81061875.pdf&d=vZqP73C4vtVS24xoHJ2BqU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=be32ae52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www-pub.iaea.org/MTCD/Publications/PDF/Pub1660web-81061875.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"292df3bae388b0713575ece233587988292d5a66","tid":531782,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ca5b88efa29e34d1b78b4af28685fc64177e107","tid":531782,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"4.2.3開始睇"},{"pid":"f0d29c93e6682d38fd68b6342185765a1e783128","tid":531782,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6fae9c933bc360145837110220cdff31845db6","tid":531782,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"Nana<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9681bd7b003a4e4f72aa769